{"tid":2205416,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–精準控制液體流動的手段","createTime":"2020-09-16T21:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T11:39:54.000Z","uid":38861,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fc144f4599fb86e247c21542824a7c224a2f6a25","tid":2205416,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:04:59.000Z","msg":"要準確地移動固體並不是難事，但要精準控制液體流動的話就絕對不簡單了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBkScnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBkScnY.jpg&h=0b226e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）近日香港大學的科學家們研發出一種三層物料（Ref1)，展示出精準控制液體流動的手段。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYrNLH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYrNLH1.jpg&h=d65594f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物料的外層為排斥液體層，只要液體的體積控制在一定的程度下，水、酒精及各式各樣的液體將會被鎖定為水珠狀，不會仙女散花灑在地上。<br />\n<br />\n而物料的中心層則有著把熱力轉化成為電力的特質，底層則有光線轉化成熱力的特性。<br />\n<br />\n當利用激光照射到物料後，底層的物料便會將光線轉化成為熱能，其熱力將會在中心層轉化為為電能，而中心層電能的電極則會吸引位於上層的液體水珠前來。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）利用這個機制，他們可以任意操控液體的移動方向，使水珠反地心吸力行走，甚至是把兩顆水珠混合在一起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqqVUBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqqVUBp.jpg&h=edf20066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）把水珠混合在一起後，他們亦有能力把水珠一分為二，甚至能精準切割水珠的大小。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9vZBPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9vZBPN.jpg&h=4713f798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）如果利用水珠製成「汽車」輪胎的話，甚至可以利用激光引領「汽車」行走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfTHzBv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfTHzBv.jpg&h=167417d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在越來講求精準的時代，這種控制液體的手法將會帶來無窮的可能性。舉例來說，科學家可以透過光線調控腐蝕性液體與物件接觸的時間、研究多種液體混合的化學作用等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=92f6c82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=d6f28952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/6/38/eabc1693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadvances.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F6%2F38%2Feabc1693&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=d6a2eba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/6/38/eabc1693</a>"},{"pid":"a894e6341ae21a7b1dee2d1b72be0cd42b5a6810","tid":2205416,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:07:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6b09196223994ddc5898b982735e4ac96c83565","tid":2205416,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6bb46962e6407bcab8256e1f3d3412da13fe6